#: ../../source/deployment-guide/storage.rst:447
msgid "Application Level Replication"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment-guide/storage.rst:449
msgid ""
"Yet another means to provide redundancy of data is to use application- level"
" replication where available."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deployment-guide/storage.rst:452
msgid ""
"Famous examples include database server replication, where one or more MySQL"
